22
00:02:51.221 --> 00:02:53.381
[Host] 好吧。啊？

23
00:02:53.731 --> 00:03:05.803
[Guest] 总之，我在 LinkedIn 上的真实名字是“Yemi debugging the Dark Candy，the mobile development ordinary first of his name”。哎呀。应该是“his name of first ordinary development mobile”。

24
00:03:06.153 --> 00:03:10.377
[Host] Bubble the candy dark the in debugging yummy Jacob Chantling

25
00:03:10.727 --> 00:03:12.047
[Guest] 哈哈哈哈。

26
